        d="M 200.8 70 L 200.8 67.1 L 240.2 67.1 L 240.2 7.2 L 217.7 55.4 L 195.2 7.1 L 195.2 70.1 L 192.2 70 L 192.2 0 L 195.2 0 L 217.7 48.3 L 240.2 0.1 L 243.2 0 L 243.2 70.1 L 200.8 70 Z M 121.7 3.1 L 59.1 3.1 L 59.1 0.1 L 126 0.1 L 100.5 70.2 L 87.5 34.6 L 74.6 70.2 L 49.1 0.1 L 52.3 0.1 L 74.6 61.4 L 87.5 25.8 L 100.5 61.4 L 121.7 3.1 Z M 139.4 70.1 L 139.4 67.1 L 176.2 67.1 L 155 8.8 L 132.7 70.1 L 129.5 70.1 L 155 0 L 180.5 70.1 L 139.4 70.1 Z M 39.8 0.1 L 44.1 0.1 L 10.5 33.5 L 47.3 70.1 L 43 70.1 L 6.2 33.5 L 39.8 0.1 Z M 0 0.1 L 3 0.1 L 3 70.1 L 0 70.1 L 0 0.1 Z M 266 0.1 L 266 70.1 L 263 70.1 L 263 0.1 L 266 0.1 Z"
